<p>Postpartum sex: Meanwhile, Nikki opened up about their postpartum sex life on the Bellas Podcast : 'I didn’t even make it to the six-week point, I just started at five. I was like I’m healed, I’m fine'</p>

<p>Meanwhile, Nikki opened up about their postpartum sex life on the Bellas Podcast: 'I didn’t even make it to the six-week point, I just started at five. I was like I’m healed, I’m fine.'</p>

<p>She added that the experience felt 'a little different': 'I felt like organs were about to drop out. I was like, shoot, did I mess up?'</p>

<p>They welcomed their first child on July 31, announcing the news on Instagram: '7/31/2020 Our baby boy is here and we couldn’t be HAPPIER and more in LOVE! Everyone is safe and healthy.' </p>

<p>She gave birth just a day before twin sister Brie Bella, 36, welcomed her own son Buddy Dessert, one month, also sharing daughter Birdie Joe, three, with husband Daniel Bryan, 39.</p>

